This is a technical preview of what will be the upcoming version of Nitrocid KS 0.2.0. Many features, which may make it to the final release early next year, are missing.

We can't provide an exact ETA for the final release, but contributions, feedback, and suggestions are welcome.

### Changes

This release contains a variety of changes, including, but not limited to:

- `[+]` Added new screensavers
- `[+]` Added Chatbot AI (uses ChatGPT, supports GPT-5 (paid only))
- `[*]` Updated to Terminaux 7.0
- `[*]` Restructured the language management to use LocaleStation
- `[*]` Addons and mods are split into two separate folders: important and extras `*`
- `[*]` Fixed splash closing issue if using the custom splash
- `[*]` Build system improvements
- `[*]` General improvements and bug fixes
- `[-]` Removed Nitrocid-specific console writers
- `[-]` Removed duplicate code as a result of migration of some features to Terminaux 7.0

Legend:

- Changes highlighted with a `*` at the end indicate that they're backported for 0.1.0 and 0.1.2.
- Changes highlighted with a `+` at the end indicate that they're backported for 0.1.2.

Review the commit history if you want to get a deep insight about the changes.

### Feedback?

If you have issues with this version, report to us by [making a new issue ticket](https://gitlab.com/aptivi/main/Nitrocid/-/issues/new).

